Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:08.65,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好暗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:11.19,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好暗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:14.48,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好~暗~啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:15.79,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:16.82,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:20.67,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}以前好像有過類似的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:25.38,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}這裏比以前那裏要亮多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:29.45,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}聽到好像有甚麼東西在動着的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.81,0:00:32.49,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}{\fs48\pos(1185,1002)}活着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.81,0:00:32.49,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}這裏的設備說不定還運作着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:35.15,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:01.06,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:00.36,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我說 活着是怎麼一回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.80,0:01:05.42,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不是 我說的是機器能工作的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:08.84,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不是作為生命體存活着的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.87,0:01:13.26,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}那 生命體是甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:17.59,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}生命體應該就是生物…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:21.58,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}是甚麼來着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:45.10,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}生命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:16.92,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}小千？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.58,0:02:18.34,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}安靜些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:01.49,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我說 你覺得剛剛的是甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.36,0:03:04.86,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}感覺…總之是很大的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:06.69,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}詞彙量太少了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:09.49,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}那個是生物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:11.51,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}嗯…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:13.33,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}應該不算是生物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:16.78,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}怎麼看都是機器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:22.33,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}況且機器不會呼吸也沒有意識
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:25.28,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}跟我們乘坐的車子是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:29.04,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}機械不會憑意志行動或者思考
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:33.49,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}但是剛才那傢伙應該是自己在走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:36.70,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}說不定是有誰在操作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:42.29,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}那麼 如果有個機器獨自走了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:44.99,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}還向我們打招呼說「你好」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.50,0:03:47.34,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不存在那種機器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.31,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}而且別說機器了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:04:02.87,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}據說地球上已經不存在人類以外的生物了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:12.77,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不存在生物…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:15.45,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.39,0:04:21.09,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:22.28,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}魚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:26.58,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}還活着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:27.89,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}存在的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:39.28,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}小千
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:52.88,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:04.08,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}誒~ 沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:05.36,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:08.01,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}那是我負責管理的魚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:10.62,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不能受到局外人的干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:13.06,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}果然是魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:16.62,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不允許食用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:21.33,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}話說回來 機器竟然在說話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:26.13,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你到底是甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:29.50,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我是負責管理這片區域的自律型機器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:33.42,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}請放心 我不會加害你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:36.84,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}很好 那我們強行搶來吃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:38.33,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:39.35,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}請別這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:43.19,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}原本為了應對有攻擊性的局外人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:45.45,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我能夠呼叫警備機器過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:46.81,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:47.93,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}可是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:50.33,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}現在通信中斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:52.28,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:53.04,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:58.31,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}警備機器就是我們來的路上看到的那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:05:59.81,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}那個大傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.14,0:06:04.24,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不 那個應該是負責整修這片區域的建設機器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:07.99,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}這附近還能運作的只有我和它了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:13.69,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}古代人的技術還能造出這些機器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:17.32,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}這些東西到底是怎麼造出來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:23.72,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我們不會把魚吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:27.29,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}能告訴我們更多關於機器 還有這裏的一切嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:29.82,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}可以哦 我來給你們帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:35.88,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我說 說話就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.40,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我想吃那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:38.20,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:41.41,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}啊 魚魚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:53.60,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}感覺像在水中一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:56.59,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}這裏是最大的水槽的正下方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:07:00.69,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}真好 好想泡在這麼多的水裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:02.32,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}要進去試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:05.06,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}做得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.66,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}可以在未使用的水槽裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:11.22,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}這個設施裏有102個水槽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:13.70,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}現在能運作的有十二個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:15.43,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}使用中的只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:18.24,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}使用中的是剛才的那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:19.51,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:23.09,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}也就是說 其他水槽裏沒有魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:24.12,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.41,0:07:29.37,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}這裏曾是大量生產食用魚的生產設施
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:30.66,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}大量地…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:33.64,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}但是如今只剩下那一條了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:35.06,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:36.20,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不允許食用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:37.67,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:42.54,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}這裏的水槽可以隨你們使用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:10.87,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}呼吸…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:24.02,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}哦 浮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.21,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:31.78,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}啊 累了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:35.63,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}吶 既然累了就去把魚吃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:36.29,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:38.21,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}都說不可以了聽到沒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:39.08,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:51.99,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:53.46,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我說 優
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:55.34,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}之前看到的那條魚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:57.78,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}應該就是從這裏衝下去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:00.07,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}洗衣服的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:02.74,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}啊 那條很好吃的魚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:07.98,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}等等 別在這裏洗衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:11.37,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}會把水弄髒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:14.56,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我還在游泳呢 注意點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:16.92,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不 你也幫下忙呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:19.64,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:20.69,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}嘖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:23.12,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}環境污染 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:27.50,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}在過去 地球就是一個巨大的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:31.02,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}人類卻選擇從中獨立出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:35.68,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}他們代替水 空氣和能量的循環
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:40.29,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}建造了能持續提供人類生存環境的都市
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:42.87,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}要讓在都市基層中設置的這些基礎設施
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:46.15,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}儘可能地維持運作下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:47.91,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}就是我們的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:50.66,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}即使人類已經不復存在了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:53.11,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}這對我們來說沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:55.34,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我們只負責維持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:59.62,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我說 小千也進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:01.46,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}很暖和哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:04.97,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}那傢伙為甚麼能游得這麼自由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:07.19,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}適應能力很高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.28,0:10:10.12,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我也去游一遊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:16.56,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:19.53,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}為甚麼要穿內衣 全裸就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:21.67,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不是…這裏還有人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:25.59,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}那是機器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:26.99,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}雖然沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:38.39,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}腳…腳碰不到底
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:40.07,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好啦 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.08,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}給我等下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:47.11,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}這該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:49.78,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}雙腳不停踩水就能浮起來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:53.03,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}喂 竟然放開手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:54.40,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}可以的 可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:58.20,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}吸一大口氣 全身放鬆就能浮起來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:10:59.19,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:01.88,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}等…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:04.58,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}哦呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:19.73,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}大海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:21.81,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}魚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:56.66,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:02.25,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}在過去 地球就是一個巨大的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:05.43,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}如果是那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:07.74,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}現在是怎麼樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:25.82,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:29.10,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}一般來說這個是不會跳的品種
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:31.33,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}存在某種突變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:33.61,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}突變…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:37.05,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}命令的誤傳 也就是一種錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:40.39,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}也就是進化的源泉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:44.24,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}機器說的話好難理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:45.98,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}想烤了吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:47.18,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}別了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:50.63,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我說 我也可以這樣做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:53.51,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}餵食嗎 可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:54.85,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:58.36,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:01.08,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}今天還能餵五顆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:03.35,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:12.14,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}這樣的話我們是不是成為朋友了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:14.64,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}和捕食者成不了朋友的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:19.33,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好想帶着你一起去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.78,0:13:21.32,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}明明都流口水了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.81,0:13:26.29,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}今天真是累了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:29.27,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}睡覺的話可以去那邊的配管下面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:31.17,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}那邊有溫水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:36.09,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:40.70,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}一直在想他真的像活的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:42.23,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}明明是個機器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.79,0:13:45.86,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}因為我們為了可以和人類交流
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:49.27,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}配有了「共感」的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.11,0:13:52.69,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}共感是甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:56.63,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}就是你們高興的話 我也高興的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:57.86,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:08.20,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好溫暖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:09.39,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:27.09,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}甚麼聲音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:30.29,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:44.46,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}喂 優
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:47.31,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:48.98,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}{\an8}小千真是的 好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:49.56,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}喂 優
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:56.38,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}超大的那個機器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:14:58.03,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}為甚麼會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:01.37,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好像開始拆解這座設施了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:02.99,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}為甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:04.34,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:09.09,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}為了保證器材的充足會拆解多餘的設施
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:10.69,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我去問下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:12.63,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你可以和他對話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:39.82,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}會不會在吵架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:01.10,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}怎麼樣 甚麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:03.41,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}他說要拆解這一塊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:07.45,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我提議停下 他沒有聽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:08.84,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}沒用的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:09.55,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:11.37,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}那樣的話魚就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:18.23,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}周圍這一片幾乎都在拆解的範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:23.54,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}恐怕是對城市來說產生了致命的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:27.80,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}錯誤… 那也是進化的源頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:32.28,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}如果破壞後的下一輪創造也算是進化的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:57.16,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我說小千
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:03.34,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我們去救那條魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:06.26,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}但是要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:08.77,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}是我的話做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:10.87,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:11.67,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:14.39,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}如果是你們的話說不定可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:23.49,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你不是想要吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:25.96,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不是 不知道為甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:28.59,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}想要救那條魚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:32.05,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}可能這就是共感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:33.58,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:37.62,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}這些有一半的話應該就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:41.27,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}把這些炸藥裝在它的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:44.41,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}破壞了它的內部構造 就能讓它停止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:54.63,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}去上面那條通路的話能不能上它的背
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:59.29,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}從那邊爬上去的話就可以到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.06,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:03.38,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好 我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:10.63,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我不認為救下那條魚對你們有好處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:16.00,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我也不是很明白那傢伙的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:20.84,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}話說 要破壞那個超大的機器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:24.12,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}果然是殺了它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:27.09,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}這取決於對生命的定義
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:29.18,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.68,0:18:31.40,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我們都活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:34.15,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}那條魚也活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:38.68,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}巨大的機器雖然不會說話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:42.09,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}但卻可以感受到「共感」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:50.92,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}大概是因為他也活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:53.62,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.30,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}從前人和機器和都市都活着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:02.76,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}都在循環裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:07.15,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}優 再不快點的話裝魚的水槽會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:09.37,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:11.50,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:27.44,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}抱歉了 大傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.42,0:19:30.32,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}小千
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:07.55,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}看來我和魚可以多活一段時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:10.57,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}當然總有一天會死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:17.07,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}人 機器 魚 都市都是活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:20.32,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}但是也終將有一天迎來終結
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:24.28,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}小千
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:29.95,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}生命是不是意味着會有終結
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:35.91,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.87,0:20:45.01,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}雖然救下了魚 但是破壞了好多東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.73,0:20:47.34,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}還能重建嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:50.77,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}然後就可以那個了吧 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.30,0:20:52.27,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}進化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:53.76,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.49,0:20:57.35,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不行的呢 只靠我一個人的力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:21:00.12,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}只能做到堵住漏水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:03.10,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}只能維持嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:04.01,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:07.77,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}也許進化會有極限
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:12.84,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}這個城市經歷了大規模的破壞後 就一直這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:17.09,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}這一層的人類們也不知不覺地消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:22.37,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}破壞之後沒有創造的話 就只是終結了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:25.17,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:31.42,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}那我們也要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.98,0:21:34.78,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}如果你們兩位可以長壽就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:36.87,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我也希望如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.18,0:21:38.82,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}兩位請多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:40.83,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}同感
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:41.75,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}嗯
